'''第88屆奧斯卡金像獎'''（{{lang-en|88th Academy Awards}}）是[[美国电影艺术与科学学会|美国电影艺术与科学学会]]為表彰[[2015年电影列表|2015年度傑出電影]]所頒發的獎項，頒獎典禮訂於2016年2月28日下午4:00 [[PST|PST]]（下午7:00 [[EST|EST]] / 00：00 [[UTC|UTC]]）在[[加利福尼亚州|加州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]][[好莱坞|好莱坞]]的[[杜比剧院|杜比剧院]]舉行，共计颁发了24个类别的[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]（也称「学院奖」）<ref>{{cite news| url = http://oscar.go.com/news/oscar-news/when-are-the-oscars-2016-start-time-and-date-for-the-88th-academy-awards| title = When Are The Oscars 2016? Start Time and Date for The 88th Academy Awards!| work = Jim Donnelly| publisher = 学院官方网站| date = 2016-01-29| accessdate = 2016-02-01| archive-date = 2016-02-02| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160202150710/http://oscar.go.com/news/oscar-news/when-are-the-oscars-2016-start-time-and-date-for-the-88th-academy-awards| dead-url = no}}</ref>。在儀式上，由美國電影藝術與科學學院頒發24大類的[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]。頒獎典禮由[[美國廣播公司|美國廣播公司]]轉播，大卫·希尔（{{lang|en|David Hill}}）和{{tsl|en|Reginald Hudlin|雷吉纳·哈德林}}担纲制作人，格伦·魏斯（{{lang|en|Glenn Weiss}}）导演<ref>{{cite web|title=Oscars: Academy Announces Show Dates For Next Three Years, Dates For 2015–16 Season|url=http://deadline.com/2015/04/oscars-dates-announced-for-2016-2017-2018-1201407366/|first=Erik|last=Pedersen|accessdate=2015-05-23|publisher=Deadline.com (Penske Media Corporation)|date=2015-04-09|archive-date=2016-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160810094510/http://deadline.com/2015/04/oscars-dates-announced-for-2016-2017-2018-1201407366/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。演员[[克里斯·洛克|克里斯·洛克]]继2005年主持[[第77届奥斯卡金像奖|第77届典礼]]后，第二次接棒主持<ref>{{cite news|last=Oldham|first=Stuart|title=Chris Rock Confirmed to host The Oscars|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/chris-rock-oscars-host-1201623174/|accessdate=2015-10-21|work=Variety|publisher=Penske Media Corporation|date=2015-10-21|archive-date=2015-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151022140850/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/chris-rock-oscars-host-1201623174/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年11月14日，第7届{{le|理事会奖|Governors Awards}}典礼在[[好莱坞高地中心|好莱坞高地中心]]大宴会厅（{{lang|en|Grand Ballroom}}）先行举办<ref>{{cite news|last=Whipp|first=Glenn|title=Governors Awards: Academy bestows honors, announces new diversity initiative|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/goldstandard/la-et-mn-governors-awards-oscars-20151115-column.html|accessdate=2016-02-04|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2015-11-15|archive-date=2016-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160204102114/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/goldstandard/la-et-mn-governors-awards-oscars-20151115-column.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年2月13日，[[奥斯卡科技成果奖|奥斯卡科技成果奖]]在[[加利福尼亚州|加州]][[贝弗利山_(加利福尼亚州)|贝弗利山]][[比佛利威尔希尔饭店|比佛利威尔希尔饭店]]举行，[[奥利维亚·穆恩|奥利维亚·穆恩]]和[[杰森·席格尔|杰森·席格尔]]主持<ref>{{cite news|first=Huggins|last=Sarah|url=http://oscar.go.com/news/oscar-news/olivia-munn-and-jason-segel-to-host-academys-sci-tech-awards|title=Olivia Munn and Jason Segel To Host 2016 Sci-Tech Awards|accessdate=2015-01-29|work=The Academy|publisher=Oscar.org|date=2016-01-29|archive-date=2016-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160210031457/http://oscar.go.com/news/oscar-news/olivia-munn-and-jason-segel-to-host-academys-sci-tech-awards|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[疯狂的麦克斯：狂暴之路|疯狂的麦克斯：狂暴之路]]》凭借六项大奖成为当晚的大赢家，《[[聚焦_(电影)|焦点]]》赢得包括[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]在内的两项大奖。其他得奖者夺得三项大奖包括《[[荒野猎人|荒野猎人]]》和分获一项大奖的《[[河中女孩：宽恕的代价|河中女孩：宽恕的代价]]》、《[[艾米_(纪录片)|艾米]]》、《{{le|熊物语|Bear Story}}》、《[[大空头|大空头]]》、《[[间谍之桥|间谍之桥]]》、《[[丹麦女孩|丹麦女孩]]》、《[[机械姬|机械姬]]》、《[[八恶人|八恶人]]》、《[[腦筋急轉彎_(電影)|腦筋急轉彎]]》、《[[房间_(电影)|房间]]》、《[[索尔之子|索尔之子]]》、《[[007：幽灵党|007：幽灵党]]》和《[[口吃男戀語|口吃男戀語]]》。电视转播在美国获得超过3442万名观众观看，创下自2008年[[第80届奥斯卡金像奖|第80届奥斯卡金像奖]]以来的最低收视纪录。

== 入圍及得獎名單 ==
第88屆奧斯卡金像獎入圍名單於2016年1月14日，在[[加利福尼亚州|加州]][[比佛利山庄酒店|比佛利山庄酒店]]的[[塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院|塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院]]，由影視學院主席{{tsl|en|Cheryl Boone Issacs|雪莉兒·布恩·艾薩克斯|-{zh-cn:谢丽尔·布恩·艾萨克斯;zh-tw:雪莉兒·布恩·艾薩克斯;}-}}、導演[[李安|李安]]與[[葛雷摩·戴托羅|葛雷摩·戴托羅]]，以及共同[[約翰·卡拉辛斯基|約翰·卡拉辛斯基]]公布<ref name="EW noms">{{cite news|last1=Coggan|first1=Devan|title=John Krasinski, Guillermo del Toro, Ang Lee to announce Oscar nominations|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/01/11/oscars-john-krasinski-guillermo-del-toro-ang-lee|accessdate=2016-01-11|publisher=Entertainment Weekly|date=2016-01-13|archive-date=2019-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190406113333/https://ew.com/article/2016/01/11/oscars-john-krasinski-guillermo-del-toro-ang-lee/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="88nom">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-nominations-2016-full-list-855670 |title=Oscar Nominations: The Complete List |work=The Hollywood Reporter |last=Ford |first=Rebecca |date=2016-01-14 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archive-date=2019-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212191644/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-nominations-2016-full-list-855670 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。李安也是首位獲邀宣布入圍名單的華人<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160112005154-260404 |title= 首次由華人揭曉！李安將宣布奧斯卡入圍名單 |publisher= 中國時報 |date= 2016-01-12 |author= 蔣鈴鈴 |accessdate= 2016-01-13 |archive-date= 2016-02-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160202101201/http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160112005154-260404 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。《[[神鬼獵人|神鬼獵人]]》以12項提名領跑，《[[疯狂的麦克斯：狂暴之路|疯狂的麦克斯：狂暴之路]]》則以10項緊隨其後<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/jan/14/oscar-nominations-2016-the-revenant-leads-field-mad-max-in-second-place|title=Oscar nominations 2016: The Revenant leads field, Mad Max in second place|date=2016-01-14|work=Guardian|accessdate=2016-01-14|archive-date=2016-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160114151242/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/jan/14/oscar-nominations-2016-the-revenant-leads-field-mad-max-in-second-place|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[亚历杭德罗·冈萨雷斯·伊尼亚里图|亚历杭德罗·冈萨雷斯·伊尼亚里图]]执导的电影连续第二年获得最多提名。作曲家{{le|安诺尼|Anohni}}成为第二位提名奥斯卡的变性人<ref>{{cite web|title=Meet the Second-Ever Transgender Oscar Nominee|url=http://www.advocate.com/film/2016/1/14/meet-second-transgender-oscar-nominee|first=Daniel|last=Reynolds|publisher=The Advocate|date=2016-01-14|accessdate=2016-02-27|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304192548/http://www.advocate.com/film/2016/1/14/meet-second-transgender-oscar-nominee|dead-url=no}}</ref>（此前{{le|安琪拉·莫利|Angela Morley}}曾于1974年和1976年被提名）<ref>{{cite web|title=Antony Hegarty: First transgender person to be nominated for an Oscar in 30 years|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/antony-hegarty-first-transgender-person-to-be-nominated-for-an-oscar-in-30-years-a6833096.html|first=Maya|last=Oppenheim|work=Independent|date=2016-02-26|accessdate=2016-02-27|archive-date=2016-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160228032318/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/antony-hegarty-first-transgender-person-to-be-nominated-for-an-oscar-in-30-years-a6833096.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AnohniNOM"/>。

2016年2月28日，得奖者在颁奖典礼上揭晓<ref>{{cite web|title=2016 Oscars Winners List: Who Took Home a Statuette?|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2016/02/2016-oscars-winners-list|work=Vanity Fair|date=2016-02-28|accessdate=2016-02-29|archive-date=2016-02-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160229211404/http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2016/02/2016-oscars-winners-list|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《焦点》凭借两项奥斯卡奖成为自1952年《[[戏中之王|戏中之王]]》凭借另一项大奖赢得最佳影片奖以来<ref>{{cite web|title=Oscars 2016: Two Irish films win, best actor for DiCaprio|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/culture/film/oscars-2016-two-irish-films-win-best-actor-for-dicaprio-1.2554012|first=Donald|last=Clarke|work=The Irish Times|date=2016-02-28|accessdate=2016-02-29|archive-date=2016-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160301102449/http://www.irishtimes.com/culture/film/oscars-2016-two-irish-films-win-best-actor-for-dicaprio-1.2554012|dead-url=no}}</ref>的首部影片<ref>{{cite web|title='Spotlight' Wins Oscar For Best Picture; Pope Challenged By Producer From Stage|url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/spotlight-oscar-winner-best-picture-2016-academy-award-tom-mccarthy-1201710767/|first=Donald|last=Clarke|publisher=deadline|date=2016-02-28|accessdate=2016-02-29|archive-date=2016-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160301092119/http://deadline.com/2016/02/spotlight-oscar-winner-best-picture-2016-academy-award-tom-mccarthy-1201710767/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[亚历杭德罗·冈萨雷斯·伊尼亚里图|亚历杭德罗·冈萨雷斯·伊尼亚里图]]成为唯一一位墨西哥裔导演和第三位连续两年赢得[[奥斯卡最佳导演奖|最佳导演奖]]的导演（此前[[约翰·福特|约翰·福特]]和[[约瑟夫·曼凯维奇|约瑟夫·曼凯维奇]]分别于1940年至1941年和1949年至1950年获此殊荣）<ref>{{cite web|title='Spotlight' Wins Oscar for Best Picture in Hollywood's Biggest Night|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/oscars-host-chris-rock-spares-few-in-opening-monologue-1456713141|first=Ben|last=Fritz|work=The Wall Street Journal|date=2016-02-28|accessdate=2016-02-29|archive-date=2016-02-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160229063250/http://www.wsj.com/articles/oscars-host-chris-rock-spares-few-in-