== 典礼花絮 ==
[[File:Chris_Rock_WE_2012_Shankbone.JPG|120px]]主持第88屆奧斯卡頒獎典禮]]
去年典礼获得褒贬不一的评价后，{{le|尼尔·梅隆|Neil Meron}}和{{le|克雷格·贾丹|Craig Zadan}}宣布不会连续第四年回归制作节目。不久后，演员[[尼尔·帕特里克·哈里斯|尼尔·帕特里克·哈里斯]]宣布奖不再第二次主持奥斯卡<ref>{{cite news|last=Hammond|first=Pete|title=Oscars: Craig Zadan & Neil Meron Not Returning In 2016; Academy Starts New Producer Search|url=http://deadline.com/2015/03/craig-zadan-neil-meron-not-returning-oscars-2016-producers-1201399124/|accessdate=2015-09-02|publisher=Deadline.com (Penske Media Corporation)|date=2015-03-26|archive-date=2016-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160427030100/http://deadline.com/2015/03/craig-zadan-neil-meron-not-returning-oscars-2016-producers-1201399124/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在《[[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]]》发表的一篇采访中，他表示「我不知道我的家人和我的精神能不能接受得了。它是一头野兽。揭晓奖项固然有趣，但面对大量耗费的事件和可理解的武断回应，我不认为这是种每年出现或是再次出现的令人愉快的平衡<ref>{{cite web|last=Bradley|first=Bill|title=Neil Patrick Harris Doesn't Know If His 'Family Or Soul' Could Take Another Oscars|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/03/04/neil-patrick-harris-oscars_n_6795084.html|accessdate=2015-09-02|work=The Huffington Post|publisher=AOL|date=2015-03-04|archive-date=2015-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017102526/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/03/04/neil-patrick-harris-oscars_n_6795084.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」随着连任的学院主席[[谢丽尔·布恩·伊萨克斯|谢丽尔·布恩·伊萨克斯]]假定担任领导职务，学院于2015年9月聘请{{le|大卫·希尔 (制片人)|David Hill (producer)|大卫·希尔}}和{{le|雷吉纳·哈德林|Reginald Hudlin}}制作典礼。被宣布为制作人的第二天，希尔透露节目将会有两名主持人<ref>{{cite web|last=Breznican|first=Anthony|title=Oscars producer says there will be two hosts for next year's ceremony|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/09/02/oscars-2016-hosts|accessdate=2015-09-02|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2015-09-02|archive-date=2015-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150904171517/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/09/02/oscars-2016-hosts|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

然而在2015年10月，据宣布喜剧演员[[克里斯·洛克|克里斯·洛克]]奖主持电视转播节目。至于让洛克回归出任主持原因，他们给出的解释是：“克里斯·洛克是娱乐产业真正的MVP。喜剧演员、演员、编剧、制片人、导演、纪录片导演——他全包了。他将会是一位惊人的奥斯卡主持人！<ref>{{cite news|last=Verhoeven|first=Beatrice|title=Chris Rock Confirmed to Host the Oscars|url=http://www.thewrap.com/chris-rock-confirmed-to-host-oscars/|accessdate=2015-10-21|publisher=The Wrap|date=2015-10-21|archive-date=2015-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151024000239/http://www.thewrap.com/chris-rock-confirmed-to-host-oscars/|dead-url=no}}</ref>”洛克表示，他很高兴被选中再次支持晚会，并评论道：“我很高兴能主持奥斯卡，回归的感觉很棒<ref>{{cite news|title=Chris Rock to host 2016 Oscars|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-34591581|accessdate=2015-10-21|publisher=BBC News|date=2015-10-21|archive-date=2015-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151021225958/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-34591581|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

另有数人参与典礼制作。{{le|哈罗德·惠勒|Harold Wheeler}}担任音乐总监和乐团指挥<ref>{{cite news|title=Oscars: Oscars: Glenn Weiss to Direct the Show, Billy Kimball to Write|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-glenn-weiss-direct-show-867586?utm_source=twitter|accessdate=2016-02-19|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2016-02-19|archive-date=2016-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302035746/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-glenn-weiss-direct-show-867586?utm_source=twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|德里克·麦克莱恩|Derek McLane}}回归为节目设计一套新的布景和舞台设计<ref>{{cite news|title=Oscars Name Director, Production Team for Telecast|url=http://www.thewrap.com/oscars-reveal-director-production-team-for-telecast/|accessdate=2016-02-19|work=The Wrap|date=2016-02-19|archive-date=2016-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160703143538/http://www.thewrap.com/oscars-reveal-director-production-team-for-telecast/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|法蒂玛·罗宾逊|Fatima Robinson}}担任表演节目编舞<ref>{{cite news|title=Derek McLane, Fatima Robinson, Glenn Weiss Among 2016 OSCARS Production Team|url=http://www.broadwayworld.com/bwwtv/article/Derek-McLane-Fatima-Robinson-Glenn-Weiss-Among-2016-OSCARS-Production-Team-20160219#|accessdate=2016-02-19|work=Broadway World|date=2016-02-19|archive-date=2016-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160225121831/http://www.broadwayworld.com/bwwtv/article/Derek-McLane-Fatima-Robinson-Glenn-Weiss-Among-2016-OSCARS-Production-Team-20160219|dead-url=no}}</ref>。奥斯卡小金人由[[纽约|纽约]][[新温莎|新温莎]]的Polich Tallix Fine Art Foundry制作<ref>{{cite news|last1=Ayers|first1=Alexandra|last2=Friedlander|first2=Jessica|url=http://www.hvmag.com/Hudson-Valley-Magazine/Oscars-Made-in-Hudson-Valley/|title=2016 Oscar Awards Made in the Hudson Valley|work=Hudson Valley Magazine|date=2016-02-29|accessdate=2016-02-29|archivedate=2016-02-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160229233525/http://www.hvmag.com/Hudson-Valley-Magazine/Oscars-Made-in-Hudson-Valley/}}</ref>。为了进一步简化获奖感言，致辞由获奖者阅读改由屏幕[[字幕跑马灯|滚动字幕]]显示<ref name="usatoday-thankyouscroll">{{cite web|title=Can the 'thank-you scroll' save Oscar speeches?|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/02/25/thank-you-scroll-oscars-telecast/80840490/|website=USA Today|accessdate=2016-02-29|archive-date=2016-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160228195632/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/02/25/thank-you-scroll-oscars-telecast/80840490/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[沙查·巴隆·科恩|沙查·巴隆·科恩]]事前没有告诉制片人他将以阿里G而不是以本人身份出现在舞台上。他为了换上自己的衣服，把自己和妻子锁在浴室里40分钟，之后再告诉人们他食物中毒了<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-sacha-baron-cohen-academy-871690 | title=Oscars: Sacha Baron Cohen Says Academy Didn't Know He'd Present as Ali G | publisher=Hollywood Reporter | date=2016-03-01 | accessdate=2016-03-03 | archive-date=2016-03-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302094159/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-sacha-baron-cohen-academy-871690 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

