ohni on Why She's Boycotting Academy Awards | last = David | first = Ehrlich | work = Rolling Stone | date = 2016-02-25 | accessdate = 2016-02-27 | archive-date = 2016-02-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160227042955/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/trans-oscar-nominee-anohni-on-why-shes-boycotting-academy-awards-20160225 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。”[[乔治·克鲁尼|乔治·克鲁尼]]<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/george-clooney-oscars-diversity-problem_us_569e8054e4b00f3e98630c5c?fb_comment_id=947382552009847_947470692001033#f34000e398 | title = George Clooney Thinks The Oscars Are 'Moving In The Wrong Direction' | first = Julia | last = Brucculieri | work = The Huffington Post | accessdate = 2016-01-21 | archive-date = 2016-01-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160129154239/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/george-clooney-oscars-diversity-problem_us_569e8054e4b00f3e98630c5c?fb_comment_id=947382552009847_947470692001033#f34000e398 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[露皮塔·尼永奥|露皮塔·尼永奥]]<ref>{{cite news| url = http://variety.com/2016/film/news/lupita-nyongo-white-oscars-1201683878/| script-title = en:Lupita Nyong’o ‘Disappointed’ With Lack of Oscar Diversity, Calls for Change| work = Variety| date = 2016-01-20| accessdate = 2016-02-04| archive-date = 2016-05-29| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160529065619/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/lupita-nyongo-white-oscars-1201683878/| dead-url = no}}</ref>、[[维奥拉·戴维斯|维奥拉·戴维斯]]<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.ew.com/article/2016/01/21/viola-davis-speaks-out-oscars-diversity | title = The problem is not with the Oscars, the problem is with the Hollywood movie-making system, | work = Entertainment Weekly | accessdate = 2016-01-21 | archive-date = 2016-01-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160123020355/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/01/21/viola-davis-speaks-out-oscars-diversity | dead-url = no }}</ref>等演员也提到了缺乏多样性。此外，主持人[[克里斯·洛克|克里斯·洛克]]也面临着被要求辞去主持人一职的压力<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/chris-rock-drop-oscars-host-article-1.2500532|title=Could Chris Rock drop out as Oscars host over increasing calls to boycott Academy Awards?|first1=Joe|last1=Dziemianowicz|first2=Ethan|last2=Sacks|work=Daily News|date=2016-01-18|accessdate=2016-01-21|archive-date=2016-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121011138/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/chris-rock-drop-oscars-host-article-1.2500532|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.inquisitr.com/2726212/tyres-gibson-50-cent-chris-rock-pull-out-of-oscars/ | title = Tyrese Gibson, 50 Cent Want Chris Rock To Pull Out Of Oscars | first = Emily | last = Hutchinson | work = The Inquisitr | date = 2016-01-21 | accessdate = 2016-01-21 | archive-date = 2016-01-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160129053228/http://www.inquisitr.com/2726212/tyres-gibson-50-cent-chris-rock-pull-out-of-oscars/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。但洛克仍然主持典礼，还把他的开场独白聚焦于争论议题<ref>{{cite news | url = http://variety.com/2016/film/news/chris-rock-oscars-diversity-1201687097/ | title = Chris Rock Still Hosting Oscars; Monologue to Tackle #OscarsSoWhite | work = Variety | date = 2016-01-23 | accessdate = 2016-01-28 | archive-date = 2016-01-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160128110721/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/chris-rock-oscars-diversity-1201687097/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。美国总统[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]也谈到了有关争议：

{{SquoteH|w=50%|bg=#FFE5B4|bc=#EAE4C2}}<div style="text-align: left;">
